#| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                     KMonad: Razer Blackwidow 2014

  A template for Razer Blackwidow 2014 full size model with US layout.
  It differs from ANSI 100 in that Fn key replaces right Super. It acts as f24.
  Aditionaly, five macro keys are present. This template may also apply to other Razer products. 
  
  Copy out the `defsrc' layer to start your own keyboard configuration.
  Copy out the `deflayer' template to easily start a new layer with matching `transparent' buttons.

(deflayer name
